<dl id="n10143i"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n10" href="#n10143i">N10 (VI.B.16)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n10all.htm#n10143i"> 143(i)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> negrophobe</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources">When, however, the English <mark>negrophobes</mark> proceed to prove from this that such a long liar cannot be a man but a monkey, then it is&mdash;just then!&mdash;this very negro proves from his very mode of mendacity that he is a Britisher&apos;s own brother. <small> Daniel Crawford, <a name="DCTB" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#DCTB"><cite title="source">Thinking Black</cite></a> (1912) 79</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
